                <textElement markup="html">
                    <font size="8"/>
                </textElement>
                <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Declaration: </b> I declare that all the information given above is correct to the best of my knowledge. My candidature is liable to be cancelled by the university authority in case of any error, false input, or manipulation of information committed by me at any stage. I undertake to abide by all rules of the university, maintain discipline, and accept any penal measures if found defaulting.</p><br />
<p>I shall have no objection if the university authority strikes off my name from the university register should I fail to appear for personal verification on the stipulated date, or fail to attend at least 75% of total classes held during the first fourteen (14) teaching days from the date of commencement of classes.]]></text>
            </staticText>
